er-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p>The <a href=\"/index.php/Daemon_II_Blackfyre\" title=\"Daemon II Blackfyre\">king</a>! Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Ambrose_Butterwell\" title=\"Ambrose Butterwell\">Butterwell</a>, our gracious host. May the <a href=\"/index.php/Father_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Father (the Seven)\">Father</a> grant him long life and many sons. <a href=\"/index.php/Lady_Butterwell\" title=\"Lady Butterwell\">Lady Butterwell</a>, the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden\" title=\"Maiden\">maiden</a> bride, my darling daughter. May the <a href=\"/index.php/Mother_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Mother (the Seven)\">Mother</a> make her fertile. I shall want a grandson before <a href=\"/index.php/212_AC\" title=\"212 AC\">the year</a> is out. Twins would suit me even better, so <a href=\"/index.php/Bedding\" title=\"Bedding\">churn the butter</a> well tonight, my sweet. I give you the <a href=\"/index.php/Hand_of_the_King\" title=\"Hand of the King\">King's Hand</a>, <a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a>. May the <a href=\"/index.php/Crone_(the_Seven)\" title=\"Crone (the Seven)\">Crone</a>'s lamp light his path to wisdom.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-12\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;Lord Frey's toasts</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<blockquote class=\"templatequote\" style=\"border-left:none;\"><div class=\"templatequotetext\"><p><b>Brynden</b>: You have my leave to go as well, Lord Frey, we will speak again later.\n<br /><b>Lord Frey</b>: As my lord commands.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-13\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p></div><div class=\"templatequotecite\"><cite>&#8212;<a href=\"/index.php/Brynden_Rivers\" title=\"Brynden Rivers\">Brynden Rivers</a> and Lord Frey</cite></div>\n</blockquote>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Lord_Frey&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.00</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.01</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-2\">1.02</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-3\">1.03</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-4\">1.04</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-5\">1.05</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-6\">1.06</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-7\">1.07</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-8\">1.08</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-9\">1.09</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-10\">1.10</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rtmk.7B.7B.7B2.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B3.7